# Errors

| Error                        | Solution                                                                                                                                  |
|------------------------------|-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| **Frame.io DISCONNECTED**    | - **The Frame.io server may be down:** Check that the Frame.io server is up or try again later.                                           |
|                              | - **The camera clock is not set to the correct time and date:** Set the camera clock.                                                     |
|                              | - **The network is not configured correctly:** Check the settings of the connected network.                                               |
|                              | - Turn the camera off and then on again.                                                                                                  |
|                              | - Contact the network administrator.                                                                                                      |
| **UNEXPECTED ERROR HAS OCCURRED** | - Turn the camera off and then on again.                                                                                                  |
|                              | - Contact the network administrator.                                                                                                      |
